- Update Ansible/teamserver/teamserver.yml to install havoc correctly with go latest version (sudo snap install go --classic and export PATH=$PATH:/snap/bin/go/bin)
- Edit /etc/ssh/sshd_config to:

```
  X11Forwarding yes
  X11DisplayOffset 10
  X11UseLocalhost no
```

- Check if teamserver can be started with a profile without doing it manually (./havoc server --profile ./profiles/havoc.yaotl -v --debug)
- Install havoc client on bastion host
- Change bastion host instace type to t3.medium
